prodNameC: “詩干地巴底”總原態副甲狀腺激素放射免疫分析試劑(標幟試管)
ingredientsDesc:
1.PTH Calibrators：One set of calibrators consists of seven vials containing lyophilized human serum with nominal PTH concentration.
2.PTH Controls：One set of controls consists of two vials containing PTH in lyophilized human serum with 0.1% (w/v) sodium azide.
3.Total Intact PTH tracer：One set of tracer consists of two bottles of I-125-anti PTH (1-34). Each bottle contains polyclonal goat anti PTH (1-34) which is labeled with I-125 and dissolved in 5 ml phosphate buffered saline with sodium azide 0.1% (w/v) and protein stailizers. The maximum radioactivity in a bottle is＜370 kBq (＜10μCi) .
4.PTH (39-84) antibody Coated Tubes：2 packages of 50 tubes each plus desiccant. The tubes are coated with polyclonal goat anti-PTH (39-84). The desiccant contains silica.
5.Wash Concentrate：One bottle contains 30 ml of a 30 fold concentrate of phosphate buffered saline with sodium azide 1.5% (w/v) and detergent.
applicantName: 泰歷藥品儀器股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 本產品用於定量檢測血液檢體之總原態副甲狀腺素激素(Total Intact PTH)的含量。
